          "text": "int isqrt(int n)\n{\n\tint x;\n\tint x1;\n\n\tif (n < 1)\n\t\treturn 0;\n\n\tx = 1;\n\tif (n != 1) {\n\t\tunsigned int u = (unsigned int)n + 1U;\n\t\tunsigned int s = (unsigned int)n + (u >> 31) + 1U;\n\n\t\tx1 = (int)s;\n\t\tx1 >>= 1;\n\n\t\tif (x1 >= n)\n\t\t\treturn n;\n\n\t\tdo {\n\t\t\tunsigned int t;\n\n\t\t\tx = x1;\n\t\t\tt = (unsigned int)(n / x) + (unsigned int)x;\n\t\t\tt += t >> 31;\n\t\t\tx1 = (int)t;\n\t\t\tx1 >>= 1;\n\t\t} while (x1 < x);\n\t}\n\n\treturn x;\n}",
